"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1946522-Olympic-Rebecca-Cheptegei-death-Dickson-Ndiema\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The former partner ofOlympicmarathon runner Rebecca Cheptegei has died in hospital after allegedly setting her on fire, but injuring himself in the process.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 53, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.9984894622603547, \"rank\": 0.0015128229151594537, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week,it was confirmed that Cheptegei had died four days after sustaining burns to 80 per cent of her body.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ugandan athlete was allegedly attacked following her return to Kenya, where she lived, after competing at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 0.9999999978610958, \"rank\": 1.6872742337937064e-09, \"text\": \"Ugandan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}, {\"begin\": 339, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999996746283, \"rank\": 2.7541059797283035e-10, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dickson Ndiema, her former boyfriend, was alleged to have poured a can of petrol over her before setting her alight.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"score\": 0.9994304117405739, \"rank\": 0.00048033613749502143, \"text\": \"Dickson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ndiema also sustained burns across much of his body and died in hospital on Monday, according toNation Africa.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They both spent several days in intensive care at the Moi Teaching and Referral Hospital in western Kenya.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 730, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999996746283, \"rank\": 2.7541059797283035e-10, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was reported that Cheptegei and Ndiema had been arguing over the land that Cheptegei's house was built upon.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ndiema was said to have let himself into Cheptegei's home while she was attending church with her two children.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she returned, Ndiema allegedly set her on fire during an argument before she was rushed to hospital with severe burns on most of her body.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Local police said the couple were embroiled in a heated disagreement before the shocking incident took place.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police commander Jeremiah ole Kosiom said: \\\"The couple was heard quarrelling outside their house.\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\", \"score\": 0.9979022631770471, \"rank\": 0.002102146573238578, \"text\": \"Jeremiah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the altercation, the boyfriend was seen pouring a liquid on the woman before burning her.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The suspect was also caught by the fire and sustained serious burns.\\\"\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Usain Bolt's thoughts already clear as another 16-year-old breaks his record  Do not miss:Olympic marathon runner dies after being 'set on fire by her ex-boyfriend'  Do not miss:Channel 4 fans say same thing about Ellie Simmonds as she makes hosting debut  Cheptegei later died after suffering multiple organ failure as a result of her burns.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her death was confirmed by the Ugandan Athletics Federation, who said: \\\"We are deeply saddened to announce the passing of our athlete, Rebecca Cheptegei, early this morning who tragically fell victim to domestic violence.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 0.9999999978610958, \"rank\": 1.6872742337937064e-09, \"text\": \"Ugandan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}, {\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.9984894622603547, \"rank\": 0.0015128229151594537, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a federation, we condemn such acts and call for justice.\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"May her soul rest in peace.\\\"\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Lord Coe, president of World Athletics, added: \\\"Our sport has lost a talented athlete in the most tragic and unthinkable circumstances.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2422, \"end\": 2437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999436791492026, \"rank\": 5.632402311957724e-05, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rebecca was an incredibly versatile runner who still had lots left to give on the roads, mountains and cross country trails.\\\"\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2535, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.9984894622603547, \"rank\": 0.0015128229151594537, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheptegei remains the Ugandan record holder for the women's marathon and was a former world champion in mountain running.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She represented her country at several world championships in multiple disciplines and finished in 44th place in the women's marathon at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3073, \"end\": 3086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.076351402636574e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3122, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.076351402636574e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"